Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.71,0:00:03.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since the powers of the Soul Reaper\Nwere thrust upon me,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.80,0:00:05.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,my whole world has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.85,0:00:07.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’m Substitute Soul Reaper,\NIchigo Kurosaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.69,0:00:11.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I wield this sword\Nwith all of my soul and strength
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.77,0:00:14.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,to protect my precious friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.87,0:00:25.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You are my one and only.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.83,0:00:31.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No one can take your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.56,0:00:36.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Never fade, my only flower.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.69,0:00:50.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The sun never blinds you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.03,0:00:55.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You are like a flower that blooms in shade.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.40,0:01:05.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Exhale those feelings you hold inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.18,0:01:15.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You are my one and only;\Nnow and forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.03,0:01:25.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The day may come\Nwhen all will rise against us,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.69,0:01:30.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but I will protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.59,0:01:34.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Never give up, my only flower.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.67,0:01:41.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,TIME NOTICE THAT\NYOU SHOULD NOTICE THAT
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.40,0:01:45.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,NOTICE THAT THERE’S NO OTHER
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.56,0:02:15.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Bount.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.37,0:02:17.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Bount?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.73,0:02:21.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This reishi is probably from a Bount…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.64,0:02:23.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So what's a Bount?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.45,0:02:32.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,When I was in the Department of Research\Nand Development,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.28,0:02:35.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I saw residue that looked\Na lot like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.83,0:02:40.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's a mysterious reishi that reacts\Nwith special components of human souls…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.57,0:02:46.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Upon investigation,\NI found a tribe called the Bount.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.12,0:02:47.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A tribe?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.59,0:02:49.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They are few in number,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.24,0:02:51.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but the Bount are humans\Nwho have special powers…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.56,0:02:53.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,like the Quincy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.77,0:02:58.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Quincies, having the power\Nto destroy Hollows,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.48,0:03:01.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,brought disaster\Nupon themselves, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.88,0:03:06.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Bounts absorb human souls\Nas nourishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.28,0:03:11.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Also, Quincies are born human\Nand die human, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.84,0:03:17.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,By absorbing human souls,\NBounts can live forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.24,0:03:20.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's all I found out,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.59,0:03:24.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but I have never been able\Nto see one myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.28,0:03:26.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Live forever--?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.98,0:03:28.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.48,0:03:33.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Bounts gain eternal life\Nby absorbing human souls for food.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.13,0:03:35.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's the kind of tribe they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.35,0:03:37.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that depending\Non the era and place,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.45,0:03:39.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,they were also called vampires…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.94,0:03:44.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The way Bounts usually do things is\Nto come and steal
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.41,0:03:47.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,the soul of a human who died\Nwhile konso is being performed on it…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.74,0:03:49.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But this time…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.05,0:04:05.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop a man and a woman\Nfrom having a good time together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.48,0:04:07.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You were trying to\Nsuck out his soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.48,0:04:10.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.91,0:04:13.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You'll find out in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.79,0:04:20.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Bount I saw was trying to\Nabsorb the soul of a living person…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.65,0:04:25.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What happens to people\Nif their souls are sucked out?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.37,0:04:27.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The same thing as when\Ntheir lives are taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.93,0:04:29.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The result is, in other words…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.12,0:04:30.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,death.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.87,0:04:32.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Death…?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.63,0:04:37.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We're still not sure\Nif it's a Bount.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.88,0:04:40.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do you suppose that it could be\Na subspecies of Bount?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.77,0:04:43.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, who knows…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.59,0:04:51.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you crossing your arms\Nand thinking so hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.52,0:04:53.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, there may be more victims!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.85,0:04:56.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right!\NJust as I expected of you, Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.08,0:04:58.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You sure have a strong sense\Nof justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.08,0:04:59.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Cut the sarcasm…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.24,0:05:02.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So anyway…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.04,0:05:03.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Lirin.\N– Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.56,0:05:05.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Go to Kurosaki's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.82,0:05:07.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What? No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.10,0:05:09.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.37,0:05:14.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki, Inoue, and Sado\Nwill act as support.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.62,0:05:15.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Support?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.75,0:05:21.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,These three mod souls have\Nreishi sensor functions attached.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.75,0:05:23.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sensors?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.16,0:05:26.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They can detect reishi waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.23,0:05:31.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, the enemy\Nis targeting living humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.92,0:05:35.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All of you have exceptionally\Nhigh abilities for humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.57,0:05:38.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You would be tempting prey for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.66,0:05:40.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We're not sure if they'll notice you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.62,0:05:43.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We have to find the location\Nof the enemy quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.38,0:05:46.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm… I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.63,0:05:48.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What? Huh? Then what about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.72,0:05:51.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh… It's as I just said…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.88,0:05:53.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have any abilities!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.85,0:06:00.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's right…isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.90,0:06:02.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now then…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.16,0:06:05.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So Kurodo will go to Inoue's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.44,0:06:07.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess it can't be helped…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.40,0:06:09.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're leering. You're leering…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.10,0:06:10.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.32,0:06:13.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Noba, go to Sado's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.88,0:06:17.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's the point in closing\Nyour mask?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.31,0:06:20.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.54,0:06:24.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But…don't give me too much trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.48,0:06:27.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What did you say?!\NYou're causing me trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.19,0:06:32.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? I forget, who couldn't\Ndefend against my attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.33,0:06:34.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.72,0:06:38.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You never shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.64,0:06:40.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Also, you may already know,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.67,0:06:44.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to hide yourselves\Nin stuffed animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.31,0:06:46.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stuffed animals?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.17,0:06:48.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.14,0:06:53.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.72,0:06:59.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Detect reishi waves…huh--?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.68,0:07:02.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,When did you add that sort\Nof search function?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.92,0:07:04.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that--?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.56,0:07:07.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You know what they say,\N“A stitch in time saves nine!”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.05,0:07:11.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You act as if you knew that\Nthe Bounts would come…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.71,0:07:13.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're just thinking too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.97,0:07:18.94,OS,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Seireitei Library
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.25,0:07:39.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Captain! Captain Kyoraku!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.73,0:07:43.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There is a message from\NCaptain Ukitake saying
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.74,0:07:46.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,that he wants you to hurry\Nto the Central Library.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.72,0:07:50.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Captain?! You're awake, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.16,0:07:53.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you speak in such\Nan unrefined voice…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.18,0:07:56.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's a waste of your beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.22,0:07:59.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Were you listening to\Nwhat I was saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.32,0:08:01.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I was listening…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.88,0:08:03.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably some crude work, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.96,0:08:07.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that the material concerning\Nthe item we're investigating has been lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.61,0:09:07.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.14,0:09:10.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you both so quiet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.08,0:09:12.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Someone might think it's some sort\Nof broadcasting accident!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.01,0:09:17.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look at me like\Nyou've seen something unusual!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.80,0:09:21.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The three of us are here,\Nso shall we form a trio? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.06,0:09:24.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.42,0:09:29.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Will you listen?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.70,0:09:32.87,OS,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki Clinic
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.68,0:09:32.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.87,0:09:35.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.08,0:09:36.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you say so…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.96,0:09:39.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The only stuffed animals remaining\Nin this house are the really old ones
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.85,0:09:42.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,that Yuzu and Karin had\Nwhen they were really young…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.59,0:09:43.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– No!\N– Oww!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.90,0:09:44.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, you…!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.94,0:09:47.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate,\NI can't believe that
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.10,0:09:50.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,you're trying to force me\Ninto these ratty and ugly things!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.75,0:09:53.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to tell Kisuke if\Nyou don't take this seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.75,0:09:57.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right… Then what kind of\Nstuffed animal would you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.72,0:10:01.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me. If I know what it is,\NI'll look for one…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.90,0:10:03.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.64,0:10:08.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Definitely…something that's smart\Nand moves quickly…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.72,0:10:12.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Something that reveals a glimpse\Nof cuteness within its beauty…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.72,0:10:14.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A bit gothic, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.67,0:10:15.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– not too formal…\N– This is a pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.95,0:10:17.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– yet not too cheap…\N– This is good enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.91,0:10:18.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.25,0:10:38.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What is this--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.22,0:10:42.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? Probably a bird…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.73,0:10:46.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.34,0:10:49.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can't change bodies\Nonce I've gone into one!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.48,0:10:52.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Is that so? How nice.\N– I'll be like this all my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.40,0:10:54.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Who is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.72,0:10:56.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What? Could it be, Lirin?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.10,0:11:00.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You've been making fun of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.36,0:11:03.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but that's just the sad nature\Nof being a mod soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.62,0:11:06.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're a talking stuffed animal like me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.52,0:11:14.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Watch how you talk…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.11,0:11:16.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in a really bad mood right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.73,0:11:18.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.50,0:11:26.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Since then, she's gotten carried away\Nand bosses me around…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.09,0:11:29.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it horrible--?\NI'm still sort of her elder!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.10,0:11:31.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.95,0:11:32.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.16,0:11:41.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Seniority is important, isn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.94,0:11:44.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm an elder of mod souls!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.57,0:11:47.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There's a proper order for things!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.57,0:11:52.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But I wanted to go to\NInoue's place if anything…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.02,0:11:55.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be held in that large chest…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.10,0:11:59.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But that damned old man!\NI'm so jealous!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.98,0:12:06.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Having such a stuffy old man\Npushed on to her probably upset Inoue!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.11,0:12:07.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Say, say, don't you think
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.76,0:12:10.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,we should see what the situation\Nis at Inoue's house?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.20,0:12:11.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No… not particu--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.40,0:12:17.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Right?! Inoue is definitely troubled!\NWe're not men if we don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.46,0:12:24.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What was that voice?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.52,0:12:28.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be…\NCould it be that Inoue is in…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.38,0:12:29.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This kind of…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.98,0:12:31.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,or that kind of…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.88,0:12:34.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,situation, is she?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.23,0:12:37.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.32,0:12:38.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Peeping isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.81,0:12:43.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not peeping! I'm just keeping\Nwatch to protect Inoue!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.20,0:12:45.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.05,0:12:47.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I can't leave this alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.39,0:12:48.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.02,0:12:59.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.00,0:13:04.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's as I thought!\NYou're really cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.20,0:13:07.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it can be cute depending\Non how you look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.53,0:13:12.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It is cute. I'm not saying anything\Nabout your aesthetics.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.18,0:13:17.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm the one inside of this, so…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.26,0:13:21.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I think you match it very well,\NMr. Kurodo…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.88,0:13:25.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's…what would you call it?\NMismatched? Like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.00,0:13:28.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.93,0:13:31.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kurodo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.07,0:13:33.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Did you feel that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.45,0:13:36.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this serious atmosphere?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.23,0:13:37.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A Bount.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.73,0:13:39.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.95,0:14:17.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They've come!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.99,0:14:19.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A Bount?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.23,0:14:23.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. They're far from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.43,0:14:42.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's a good girl…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.99,0:14:54.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.91,0:14:59.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A Soul Reaper?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.45,0:15:02.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just a substitute…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.61,0:15:05.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What business does\Na Soul Reaper Substitute have with me--?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.84,0:15:10.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let you eat the souls\Nof living people!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.27,0:15:13.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Please, don't interfere!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.23,0:15:14.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.87,0:15:20.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Where is she?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.88,0:15:22.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Over there, you slow poke!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.72,0:15:25.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,B-But…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.93,0:15:28.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.\NShe's just unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.36,0:15:32.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.27,0:15:36.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She's not as vicious\Nas we expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.27,0:15:38.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But you shouldn't let your guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.09,0:15:40.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.35,0:15:44.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What is this? How far\Ndo you plan on going?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.91,0:15:48.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We're almost there.\NWe're getting closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.08,0:15:49.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Turn right at the next corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.81,0:16:14.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me what you're planning…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.72,0:16:17.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.72,0:16:20.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that your mind\Nwould be able to comprehend
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.35,0:16:21.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,even if I told you…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.88,0:16:23.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What a bothersome kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.49,0:16:24.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it is a bother,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.97,0:16:27.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not letting you go\Nuntil I'm satisfied!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.52,0:16:31.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to fight…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.24,0:16:41.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Zeig dih! Goethe!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.45,0:16:48.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.14,0:16:50.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful! That's no ordinary fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.99,0:17:10.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.83,0:17:13.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How do you like my doll?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.05,0:17:13.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Doll?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.31,0:17:16.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshino… Did you call me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.68,0:17:19.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Goethe, please help me.\NHe's being persistent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.79,0:17:22.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's…being persistent, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.40,0:17:24.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.85,0:17:25.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.04,0:17:30.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Don't let go!\N– Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.72,0:17:45.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He turned back to normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.12,0:17:47.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.24,0:17:49.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He'll turn back to normal\Nno matter how many times you cut him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.52,0:17:53.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You…have no chance of winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.72,0:17:58.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There's…a Bount here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.75,0:18:01.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful! He should be nearby!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.36,0:18:04.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I-I want to go home already.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.72,0:18:07.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Noba?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.92,0:18:15.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Noba?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.84,0:18:21.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There's a person…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.01,0:18:37.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It seems we were too late…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.09,0:18:45.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought a person could\Ndisappear without a trace like this…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.72,0:19:06.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I've failed to greet you…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.35,0:19:08.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.11,0:19:10.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is this your doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.94,0:19:13.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My doing--?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.42,0:19:16.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I just finished a bit of a meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.00,0:19:19.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A meal--?! Stop joking!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.10,0:19:22.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Joking--? Me--?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.59,0:19:26.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't do something rude\Nlike that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.54,0:19:31.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm always deeply grateful to\Nmy food and pay my respects.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.44,0:19:33.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Food…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.73,0:19:37.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You all seem very delicious…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.31,0:19:43.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad… I'm already full for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.47,0:19:46.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So maybe some time later…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.84,0:19:48.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.39,0:19:51.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.87,0:19:55.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Bount Yoruichi saw was a woman…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.02,0:19:57.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It means that it was a different one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.87,0:20:28.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it… Where should I cut?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.00,0:20:30.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's useless to cut anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.51,0:20:32.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be true!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.97,0:20:35.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There's got to be away I can cut him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.45,0:20:39.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why you--!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.59,0:20:46.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She’s told you it's useless…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.89,0:20:50.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What about it?\NDo you have a better idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.75,0:20:53.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Did you forget what Kisuke\Ntold you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.36,0:20:56.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stay calm in battle…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.32,0:20:59.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Observe your opponent\Nand find a weakness!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.02,0:21:02.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stay calm…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.12,0:21:02.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's right…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.48,0:21:05.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Observe well…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.45,0:21:07.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Find…a weakness…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.94,0:21:09.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.64,0:21:10.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Hold on…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.98,0:21:23.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.04,0:21:24.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,His weak spot was his heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.94,0:21:26.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I did it, Lirin! Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.94,0:21:28.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In front of you! Look in front of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.93,0:21:36.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I told you…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.77,0:21:39.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Goethe, finish him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.76,0:21:46.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Finish him? I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.01,0:21:48.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.90,0:21:51.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right? Can you move?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.92,0:21:53.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.98,0:21:56.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need for that! Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.14,0:21:59.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.07,0:22:01.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Whoa! What the--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.72,0:22:04.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.35,0:22:06.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.62,0:22:07.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.90,0:22:24.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, fool?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.48,0:22:35.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.66,0:22:40.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Count one! And move on
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.30,0:22:42.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Count two! And take a break
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.99,0:22:45.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Count three! And think through
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.49,0:22:48.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll just go at my own pace
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.75,0:22:55.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Time goes by, and I get left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.59,0:22:58.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But I say,\N“don’t forget that anxious feeling”
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.09,0:23:00.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They tell me,\N“A reckless challenge is meaningless”
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.66,0:23:03.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But I say “don’t give up.”
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.19,0:23:13.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,(Offense!) At times when\Nthe going gets tough, I raise my voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.20,0:23:22.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,(Offense!) And head toward\Nthe direction of my goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.75,0:23:32.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There is nothing to be afraid of\Nthat towering wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.86,0:23:42.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Never losing sight in this life\Nwithout answers
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.95,0:23:45.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Keep My Pace
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.67,0:23:56.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Count one! And move on
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.17,0:23:58.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Count two! And take a break
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.78,0:24:00.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Count three! And think through
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.24,0:24:05.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll just go at my own pace
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.12,0:24:10.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Rukia Kuchiki,\Nthe transfer student.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.35,0:24:12.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get back to our school life\Nwith spirit once more!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.96,0:24:14.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.40,0:24:17.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Karakura High School arc starts\Nfrom the next episode of Bleach!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.05,0:24:20.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tune in to our bittersweet\Nyouth-filled heartfelt story!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.70,0:24:22.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That’s not what it's about!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.79,0:24:33.80,OS,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Golden Illustrated Guide to\NSoul Reapers after these messages!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.80,0:24:36.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Illustrated Guide to Soul Reapers!\N– Golden!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.30,0:24:39.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Hitsugaya,\NI'm sorry it was a waste of time
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.50,0:24:40.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,even though you came out\Nof your way to help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.09,0:24:42.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to worry…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.86,0:24:46.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This may be linked to\Nthat bastard, Aizen.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.71,0:24:48.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,As a token of my apology
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.32,0:24:50.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,how about an assortment\Nof snacks?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.08,0:24:50.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.81,0:24:52.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They're a bit out of season, but look!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.51,0:24:56.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey… Why do you always give\Nthis stuff to me--?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.28,0:24:58.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Because we're both “Shiros”!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.46,0:25:01.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Is that all?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.86,0:25:03.73,OS,Default,0000,0000,0000,,JyuSHIRO Ukitake     ToSHIRO Hitsugaya
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.92,0:25:03.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do you need more?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.73,0:25:11.74,OS,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tune in again!